title: @Tigers Miguel Cabrera Nominated For 2015 Hank Aaron Award
text:
Press Releases @Tigers Miguel Cabrera Nominated For 2015 Hank Aaron Award 
DETROIT, Michigan – The Major League Baseball and MLB Advanced Media announced that 2015 American League batting Champion(.388 batting average), Miguel Cabrera was named the Detroit Tigers nominee for the 2015 Hank Aaron Award. Fans can vote through October 11th, 2015, at MLB.com  //woodlawnpost.com/?p=122977   6 2015. Filed under Baseball , Media
